<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan>, <expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex>s</expan> czü
                                <expan>Kurmb<ex>ur</ex>g,</expan> und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        Görgen Hutten, eins papals, und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>n,</expan>
<expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>junge<ex>n</ex></expan> Hutten und <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        ledrerin sune, <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hochw<ex>irdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz her Görg Hutt bey uns nicht sesshaft ist
                        und daz wir sein nicht mechtig sein; aber wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        die <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> besant und sie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
                        cze rede gesaczt und hat uns <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Hutt gesagt, wie er
                        etlichen <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> reten <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> sache <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>und sie <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab, das</add> gen
                                <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>cze</add>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; und nu uns
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hab, so <expan>w<ex>er</ex></expan> er
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> czestund czü
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geriten, so müg er
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> nötlichs seins gescheftes
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> nicht, <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        alspald er ledig gesein müg, so wöll er czü <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hochw<ex>irdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>reit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und das <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> gen
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und wo etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Laur<ex>encii.</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
